Subject: [PATCH] media: dvb_ca_en50221: prevent using slot_info for Spectre attacs
Date: Tue, 15 May 2018 08:58:11 -0400
Message-Id: <ae2d6eda8cfc9db99fc4ce8d775fa7d4bf7d2068.1526389088.git.mchehab+samsung@kernel.org>
